Class IcaAtomEadHandler

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ContentHandler, DTDHandler, EntityResolver, ErrorHandler, LexicalHandler

    public class IcaAtomEadHandler
extends EadHandler
    Handler of EADs exported from ICA-AtoM. Only titles have to be handled in a special way. makes use of icaatom.properties with format: part/of/path/=attribute
    Author:
    Linda Reijnhoudt (https://github.com/lindareijnhoudt)
